1. U Srbiji postoji sloboda govora. (There is freedom of speech in Serbia.)
2. Država garantuje slobode i prava građanima. (The state guarantees freedoms and rights to citizens.)
3. Nema pravog života bez slobode. (There is no real life without freedom.)
4. Sloboda izražavanja je važna vrednost u demokratskom društvu. (Freedom of expression is an important value in a democratic society.)
5. *Slobodu* koju imamo u našoj zemlji treba ceniti i poštovati. (The *freedom* we have in our country should be appreciated and respected.)
6. Sloboda religije je jedno od osnovnih ljudskih prava. (Freedom of religion is one of the basic human rights.)
7. Ona je bila spremna da se bori za slobodu svoje zemlje. (She was ready to fight for the freedom of her country.)
8. Ljubav je sinonim za slobodu. (Love is synonymous with freedom.)
9. Naša borba za slobodu traje već godinama. (Our struggle for freedom has been going on for years.)
10. *Slobode* koje su nam date su ograničene zakonima i pravilima. (*Freedoms* given to us are limited by laws and regulations.)